  <title translate="true">Joint</title>
  <keywords>
    <keyword translate="true">Joints<keyword translate="true">Ball-Joint</keyword><keyword translate="true">Pin-Joint</keyword><keyword translate="true">Slide-Joint</keyword></keyword>
    <keyword translate="true">Kinematic-Pairs</keyword>
  </keywords>
  <body>
    <para styleclass="Popup Box"><table styleclass="PopupTable" rowcount="1" colcount="1">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">A </text><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">Joint</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true"> is equivalent to a </text><text styleclass="Popup Box" style="font-style:italic;" translate="true">&apos;Constraint&apos;. </text></para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">Each</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" style="font-weight:bold; font-style:italic;" translate="true">&#32;</text><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">Joint</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true"> constrains how two </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Part" styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">Parts</link><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true"> move relative to each other.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">In </text><text styleclass="VariableName-small" style="font-style:italic;" translate="true">MechDesigner</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" style="font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; font-style:italic;" translate="true">*</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">, there are three joints:</text></para>
          <list id="53" type="ul" listtype="bullet" formatstring="&#183;" format-charset="SYMBOL_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Popup Box" style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:10pt; color:#000000;">
            <li styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">A </text><text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements" translate="true">Pin-Joint</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true"> - identical to a </text><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">Revolute-Joint</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">, the </text><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">R</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true"> Joint in a </text><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">Dyad</text></li>
            <li styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">A </text><text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements" translate="true">Slide-Joint</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true"> - identical to a </text><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">Prismatic-Joint</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">, the </text><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">P</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true"> Joint in a </text><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">Dyad</text></li>
            <li styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">A </text><text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements" translate="true">Ball-Joint</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true"> - identical to a </text><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">Spherical-Joint</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">, the </text><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">S</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true"> Joint in a </text><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">Dyad</text></li>
          </list>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">The letters </text><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">R</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">, </text><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">P</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true"> and </text><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">S</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true"> refer to </text><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">R</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">evolute, </text><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">P</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">rismatic and </text><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">S</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">pherical, respectively.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#ff6600;" /></para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Popup Box" style="font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; font-style:italic;" translate="true">*</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true"> There are more joints that </text><text styleclass="VariableName-small" style="font-style:italic;" translate="true">MechDesigner</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true"> does not provide. However, they are rarely found in Packaging or Assembly Machines.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#ff6600;" /></para>
          <para styleclass="SeeAlso-small"><text styleclass="SeeAlso-small" translate="true">See also: </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Pin-Joint" styleclass="SeeAlso-small" translate="true">Pin-Joint</link><text styleclass="SeeAlso-small" translate="true">, </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Slide-Joint" styleclass="SeeAlso-small" translate="true">Slide-Joint</link><text styleclass="SeeAlso-small" translate="true">, </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Ball-Joints" styleclass="SeeAlso-small" translate="true">Ball-Joint</link></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table></para>
  </body>
